name: KaleidoBot001
description: This is the result of my current experiments with VQGan AI art, I've been loving watching all the amazing artists create with these tools. My own art has reached this level and I want to start sharing it with the community. To me these images are fragile and nearing collapse, they feel unstable and at the same time, something beautiful has emerged. I named this KaleidoBot, because my good friend says that it kinda looks like a bot, and that's pretty cool. Made with VQGan+Clip, and evolved in After Effects.
